## 2026-06-15 — project bootstrap
Repo created by extracting the Apple tools from an internal macOS probe
into a standalone Swift package + Claude skill. Dev loop is in place from day
one: `bin/build` (release), `swift test` (282 tests, live Notes gated behind
APPLE_TOOLS_NOTES_LIVE=1), and `apple-tools permissions` to front-load TCC grants.
Isolation: pure-local CLI, no server; file output confined to a private 0700
temp dir. No formal eval harness — these tools are deterministic wrappers over
macOS APIs, covered by unit + (gated) live integration tests. Checked against
agent-development.md as of this repo's first commit.
